{"id":"1b0980680f7f9aabac3bd1868a0ef20f8abc504851e254ecf67b7b7dfc94465c","item_id":"9e331b4f2c:0","text":"按给定的曝光档调整输入颜色的曝光。每个正曝光档会使输入强度加倍。每个负曝光档会使输入强度减半。通常最好使用 Exposure，而不是直接乘法（也称为增益），因为它在感知上呈线性。"}
{"id":"fc405f080fa4c1ddab9c62e4d365b50627cdde335865ae0ef372fd2dc974f944","item_id":"9e331b4f2c:3","text":"要进行曝光调整的颜色。在此连接一个颜色 pattern。"}
{"id":"877a8887947ed45b9acbe20b711ecdfc770f8c446c71a0e000cd74f231081359","item_id":"9e331b4f2c:4","text":"Stops"}
{"id":"b4b0ac8ca652f39adf92ee924e4e19eb45c8103a4e97282cae73a6a80b0173ce","item_id":"9e331b4f2c:5","text":"用于调整 inputRGB 的曝光档数量。结果会乘以 2 的 stops 次方。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:1", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "35aea6f833e7d09d9722a54bdee4bc25b02fd25547d6613ee8d9457096af94fb", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:2", "text": "Input Color"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:6", "text": "Output Parameters"}
{"id": "d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:7", "text": "resultRGB"}
{"id": "6796d2c52b4882b98311c8be5b2889976246b071d35733a80a01da19e5bcba42", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:8", "text": "钳制后的颜色结果。"}
{"id": "c9223602a8320733dcf0de118c9880f9df06acdfdb068bb26ba166fc96c52d6c", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:9", "text": "resultR"}
{"id": "c1ce276296aa97e85eded6362e0ad2b80973bc92228513facedd911006df8937", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:10", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 R 通道。"}
{"id": "2e12f103dc4a4b216b21cc6f017371b08507fc67f2a1ad9f133aa333afe0fc11", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:11", "text": "resultG"}
{"id": "009cc7a7eb8d7664fe8e8a024e817626113dd5198fc3a164f5ec297f2fa68da3", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:12", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 G 通道。"}
{"id": "c3719f180d82ecafb70ce347c3499e7668a3d9262533cadae303c770922865ff", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:13", "text": "resultB"}
{"id": "d1e2217f59ea1bd29de7ec3ac2c05c763eca2c3bf612f3e04ff7cfd536f9f8e0", "item_id": "9e331b4f2c:14", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 B 通道。"}
